

The script run_analysis.R performs the 5 steps described in the course project's definition.

Source of data that used: 

https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip

Variables

- x_train, y_train, x_test, y_test, subject_train and subject_test are the tables included in the above source data link 
- trainingdata binds the following tables y_train ,x_train, subject_train
- testdata binds the following tables y_test, x_test, subject_test
- dataset binds trainingdata,testdata tables
- dataset<-rbind(trainingdata,testdata)
